# get centroids
kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=5, random_state=0)
final12['cluster'] = kmeans.fit_predict(final12[['커피 점포 수', '5년 생존율']])

centroids = kmeans.cluster_centers_
cen_x = [i[0] for i in centroids] 
cen_y = [i[1] for i in centroids]
# cen_z = [i[2] for i in centroids]

colors = ['#DF2020', '#DFDC20',  '#81DF20', '#2095DF', '#A620DF' ] # 빨강 # 노랑 # 초록 # 파랑 # 보라

fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, figsize=(8,8))
final12['c'] = final12.cluster.map({0:colors[0], 1:colors[1], 2:colors[2], 3: colors[3], 4: colors[4]})
final12['cen_x'] = final12.cluster.map({0:cen_x[0], 1:cen_x[1], 2:cen_x[2], 3: colors[3], 4: colors[4]})
final12['cen_y'] = final12.cluster.map({0:cen_y[0], 1:cen_y[1], 2:cen_y[2], 3: colors[3], 4: colors[4]})
# final['cen_z'] = final.cluster.map({0:cen_z[0], 1:cen_z[1], 2:cen_z[2]})

In [84]:
fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, figsize=(20,20))
plt.scatter(final12['커피 점포 수'], final12['5년 생존율'], c=final12.c, alpha = 0.6, s=10)
plt.scatter(cen_x, cen_y, marker='^', c=colors, s=70)
    
for i in final12.cluster.unique():
    # get the convex hull
    points = final12[final12.cluster == i][['커피 점포 수', '5년 생존율']].values
    hull = ConvexHull(points)
    x_hull = np.append(points[hull.vertices,0],
                       points[hull.vertices,0][0])
    y_hull = np.append(points[hull.vertices,1],
                       points[hull.vertices,1][0])
    
    # interpolate
    dist = np.sqrt((x_hull[:-1] - x_hull[1:])**2 + (y_hull[:-1] - y_hull[1:])**2)
    dist_along = np.concatenate(([0], dist.cumsum()))
    spline, u = interpolate.splprep([x_hull, y_hull], 
                                    u=dist_along, s=0, per=1, )
    interp_d = np.linspace(dist_along[0], dist_along[-1], 50)
    interp_x, interp_y = interpolate.splev(interp_d, spline)
    # plot shape
    plt.fill(interp_x, interp_y, '--', c=colors[i], alpha=0.2)
    
    plt.scatter(centroids[:, 0], centroids[:, 1], marker='*', s=600,
            c= colors, label='centroid')

plt.xlabel('커피 점포 수', size = 20)
plt.ylabel('5년 생존율', size = 20)

In [101]:
fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, figsize=(20,20))
plt.scatter(final23['5년 생존율'], final23['평균영업기간(년)'], c=final23.c, alpha = 0.6, s=10)
plt.scatter(cen_x, cen_y, marker='^', c=colors, s=70)
    
for i in final23.cluster.unique():
    # get the convex hull
    points = final23[final23.cluster == i][['5년 생존율', '평균영업기간(년)']].values
    hull = ConvexHull(points)
    x_hull = np.append(points[hull.vertices,0],
                       points[hull.vertices,0][0])
    y_hull = np.append(points[hull.vertices,1],
                       points[hull.vertices,1][0])
    
    # interpolate
    dist = np.sqrt((x_hull[:-1] - x_hull[1:])**2 + (y_hull[:-1] - y_hull[1:])**2)
    dist_along = np.concatenate(([0], dist.cumsum()))
    spline, u = interpolate.splprep([x_hull, y_hull], 
                                    u=dist_along, s=0, per=1)
    interp_d = np.linspace(dist_along[0], dist_along[-1], 50)
    interp_x, interp_y = interpolate.splev(interp_d, spline)
    # plot shape
    plt.fill(interp_x, interp_y, '--', c=colors[i], alpha=0.2)
    
    plt.scatter(centroids[:, 0], centroids[:, 1], marker='*', s=600,
            c= colors, label='centroid')
    
plt.xlabel('5년 생존율', size = 20)
plt.ylabel('평균영업기간(년)', size = 20)

In [119]:
fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, figsize=(20,20))
plt.scatter(final2['5년 생존율'], final2['추정 임대료'], c=final2.c, alpha = 0.6, s=10)
plt.scatter(cen_x, cen_y, marker='^', c=colors, s=70)
    
for i in final2.cluster.unique():
    # get the convex hull
    points = final2[final2.cluster == i][['5년 생존율', '추정 임대료']].values
    hull = ConvexHull(points)
    x_hull = np.append(points[hull.vertices,0],
                       points[hull.vertices,0][0])
    y_hull = np.append(points[hull.vertices,1],
                       points[hull.vertices,1][0])
    
    # interpolate
    dist = np.sqrt((x_hull[:-1] - x_hull[1:])**2 + (y_hull[:-1] - y_hull[1:])**2)
    dist_along = np.concatenate(([0], dist.cumsum()))
    spline, u = interpolate.splprep([x_hull, y_hull], 
                                    u=dist_along, s=0, per=1)
    interp_d = np.linspace(dist_along[0], dist_along[-1], 50)
    interp_x, interp_y = interpolate.splev(interp_d, spline)
    # plot shape
    plt.fill(interp_x, interp_y, '--', c=colors[i], alpha=0.2)

    plt.scatter(centroids[:, 0], centroids[:, 1], marker='*', s=600,
            c= colors, label='centroid')  
    
plt.xlabel('5년 생존율', size = 20)
plt.ylabel('추정 임대료', size = 20)
